message: Hello future crafter! Here's what I learned: Cutting any 'soft' item gives 25 points, and framing any 'hard' item gives 20 points. The best score I found consistently was combining two 'cut' items that are both 'artificial' and 'soft' (e.g., cut yarn + cut sponge), which resulted in 50 points. Be careful with combinations; mixing 'cut' and 'framed' items or combining more than two modified items often leads to negative values. It's often safer to submit with a solid 25 or 50 points than to risk complex combinations.
